e 视频播放器" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>有趣的是，制造商 The Little Car Company 因<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/bugatty-baby-ii-electric-toy-car-015854155.html">将经典汽车缩小为较小尺寸的收藏品而</a>闻名，而不是相反。看起来该公司已经从<em>《亲爱的，我把孩子缩小了》变成</em>了<em>《亲爱的，我把孩子炸了》。</em>给他们更多的力量。</p><p>如果您在欧洲有足够的现金，您可以随电动汽车一起购买可选的公路套件，其中包括挡风玻璃、一对小型雨刷、镜子、挡泥板和可拆卸车灯。尽管这款车辆在欧洲符合四轮车的资格，因此可以注册用于道路使用，但您将无法在高速公路上携带它。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/this-ev-is-basically-an-rc-car-hit-with-a-growth-ray-170737868.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/this-ev-is-basically-an-rc-car-hit-with-a-growth-ray-170737868.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> b3483c29-dbec-4060-9372-778f90dcdaa7</guid><dc:creator>劳伦斯·邦克</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jul 2023 17:07:37 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1689010206</ingested><modified> 2023-07-10T17:30:09+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Transportation]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></category><media:content height="678" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/3c885210-1f47-11ee-adeb-bc9e466467b6" width="1200"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="678" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/3c885210-1f47-11ee-adeb-bc9e466467b6" width="1200"><med